Description for different classes

Controller.java:
Main class to call all functions written in other classes and store databse credential information.

Person.java:
Abstract model class with basic personal information.

Employee.Java:
Employee model class. Contains variables and setter and getter functions. Extends Person class.

EmployeeDBfunc.java:
Contains three funcitons. Each functions register driver, connect to DB and excute query.

EmployeeFunc.java:
Used the functions in EmployeeDBfunc.java to store, get, update, and delete employee from database.

JsonFunc.java:
Contains two funcitons, which are write an employee object to json file and read from json file and store employee object to DB.
Note: used GSON library.
